title: Family Fried Noodles | Making Noodles for a Crowd | Easy Asian Recipe
description:
Making wok-fried noodles for even a small family can be a challenge, as four serves of noodles in a wok is far too much volume for most domestic woks can handle. Try this technique to feed anything from 4 to 40 people without even breaking a sweat.
